high_descs: Go to the counter right of the stove
Pick up the knife from the counter
Go to the counter right of the sink
Cut the apple on the counter
Go to the microwave
Place the knife next to the microwave
Go to the counter right of the sink
Pick up an apple piece from the counter
Go to the microwave
Heat the apple piece in the microwave
Turn around and face the microwave
Place the apple piece next to the knife
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple piece next to a knife by a microwave

high_descs: Cross the room and face the right side of the stove so that you can see the salt and pepper shakers.
Grab the knife from the counter.
Bring the knife with you and move so that you're facing the counter to the right of the kitchen sink.
Use the knife to cut the apple that's on the counter.
Bring the knife with you over to the black microwave.
Put the knife on the table to the left of the microwave.
Go back over to where you cut the apple.
Pick up a piece of the apple from the counter.
Bring the apple with you over to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave, cook it and then take it out again.
Take a step to your left with the apple.
Put the apple down on the table to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put some warm apple on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter, then turn right and walk to the stove top.
Pick up the knife from the counter to the right of the stove top.
Turn around and walk forward until getting just past the sink on the counter, then face it.
Cut the piece of apple next to the plant in half.
Turn right, walk four steps forward then turn right and go to the microwave.
Put the knife down so it is standing up blade down just to the upper right of the spoon.
Go back to the piece of cut apple on the counter by the plant.
Pick up the closest slice of apple.
Walk back to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the apple inside and turn it it. Then take the apple out once its done and close it.
Turn left, walk on step forward and face the microwave again.
Put the apple slice down to the left of the knife and spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put the knife and microwaved sliced of apple to the left of the microwave.
